CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 15, 1960, pg. 2 reads: "At Mayors' Met, Discuss Urban Renewal - Shown at the Kennedy Conference of Urban Renewal, held Monday at the Hotel Penn-Sheraton and attended by mayors from 55 U.S. cities, were (first photo, left to right) Pittsburgh's Mayor Joseph M. Barr, Pennsylvania's Governor David L. Lawrence, New York's Congressman Adam C. Powell Jr., New York City's Mayor Robert Wagner...Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Pittsburgh Mayor Joseph M. Barr, Pennsylvania Governor David L. Lawrence, New York Congressman Adam C. Powell Jr., and New York City Mayor Robert Wagner standing in Penn-Sheraton Hotel for Kennedy Conference on Urban Renewal
